column16: Adam Duvall grounds into a double play, shortstop Jordy Mercer to second baseman Josh Harrison to first baseman John Jaso.   Joey Votto out at 2nd.
Zack Cozart reaches on a fielding error by third baseman Jung Ho Kang.   Tony Renda scores.    Billy Hamilton to 3rd.
Anthony Rizzo singles on a ground ball to left fielder Starling Marte.   Jason Heyward scores.    Kris Bryant to 3rd.
Kris Bryant walks.   Jason Heyward to 2nd.
Jason Heyward singles on a line drive to center fielder Andrew McCutchen.
